scenes.description: Performance of the song 'High Street Time' by all hololive Indonesia members.
Scene transition showing the exterior of the venue stage.
MC section where the members talk about their performance and new outfits on the school festival stage.
Graphic transition featuring the 'Gebyar hololive Indonesia' logo.
Performance of the song 'Melompat Lebih Tinggi' by the Gen 2 unit.

subtitles.original: ...Langkah kembali, melompat dan terbang lebih tinggi.
subtitles.english: ...Step back, jump and fly higher.

subtitles.original: Kejar mimpi tanpa henti, hololive ID!
subtitles.english: Keep chasing dreams, hololive ID!

subtitles.original: With Area 15! Risu, Moona, Iofi!
subtitles.english: With Area 15! Risu, Moona, Iofi!

subtitles.original: Dan juga Holoro! Ollie, Anya, Reine!
subtitles.english: And also Holoro! Ollie, Anya, Reine!

subtitles.original: Jangan lupa HoloHeroes! Zeta, Kaela, Kobo!
subtitles.english: Don't forget HoloHeroes! Zeta, Kaela, Kobo!

subtitles.original: We fly far, High Street Time, hololive ID!
subtitles.english: We fly far, High Street Time, hololive ID!

subtitles.original: Hore!
subtitles.english: Hooray!

subtitles.original: Terima kasih teman-teman! Yang barusan...
subtitles.english: Thank you, everyone! That just now...

subtitles.original: ...adalah High Street Time!
subtitles.english: ...was High Street Time!

subtitles.original: Meski terus diserang oleh badai dan hujan...
subtitles.english: Even if we're constantly struck by storms and rain...

subtitles.original: Jadi gimana guys kesan kalian saat kalian perform High Street Time?
subtitles.english: So guys, what are your thoughts on performing High Street Time?

subtitles.original: Seru! Seru banget!
subtitles.english: Fun! It was so fun!

subtitles.original: Kantan, kantan.
subtitles.english: Easy, easy.

subtitles.original: Oh, kantan dia bilang! Mau koreo yang lebih susah?
subtitles.english: Oh, she said easy! Do you want harder choreography?

subtitles.original: Nah teman-teman, kalian sadar nggak kita lagi perform di tempat yang berbeda lho!
subtitles.english: Well guys, do you realize we're performing in a different place!

subtitles.original: Iya! Wah ada benderanya!
subtitles.english: Yeah! Whoa, there are flags!

subtitles.original: Iya, kita tampil di Gebyar hololive Indonesia Pentas Seni stage!
subtitles.english: Yes, we're performing on the Gebyar hololive Indonesia School Festival stage!

subtitles.original: Lihat deh, lihat deh! Kamera, kamera!
subtitles.english: Look, look! Camera, camera!

subtitles.original: Keren banget! Gede banget! SDN Pondok Man... eh SMA ya?
subtitles.english: So cool! It's huge! SDN Pondok Man... oh wait, it's high school, right?

subtitles.original: SMA Pondok ID! Gede banget! Playground, playground!
subtitles.english: Pondok ID High School! It's so big! Playground, playground!

subtitles.original: Ada Udin terbang tadi! Ada Tata juga di depan!
subtitles.english: There was a flying Udin just now! Tata's also in front!

subtitles.original: Terus bukan cuman stage aja yang baru, tapi baju kita juga ada yang baru juga!
subtitles.english: And it's not just the stage that's new, we have new outfits too!

subtitles.original: Iya, kita pakai baju putih abu-abu, bukan batik lagi!
subtitles.english: Yes, we're wearing grey and white uniforms, no longer batiks!

subtitles.original: Ya, ini sampai ada logonya juga di belakang!
subtitles.english: Yeah, there's even a logo on the back!

subtitles.original: Sakti! Sakti!
subtitles.english: Powerful! Powerful!

subtitles.original: Nah itu apa lagi!
subtitles.english: Now what's that!

subtitles.original: Namanya juga Gebyar ya, memang harus bergebyar-gebyar holoID! Heboh heboh heboh!
subtitles.english: Well, it's called Gebyar, so holoID must be glamorous! Exciting times!

subtitles.original: Nah, terus habis itu kan tadi kita udah medley, kita udah holoID intro...
subtitles.english: So, after that, we already did the medley and the holoID intro...

subtitles.original: Tapi masih ada nih. Apa nih?
subtitles.english: But there's still more. What is it?

subtitles.original: Bagian unit!
subtitles.english: The unit section!

subtitles.original: Iya, jadi berikutnya kita bakal ada unit-unit yang bakal nyanyi bareng!
subtitles.english: Yes, so next we'll have units singing together!

subtitles.original: Kalian tau nggak kira-kira siapa yang bakal nyanyi?
subtitles.english: Do you have any idea who's going to sing?

subtitles.original: Gen 1 kah? Gen 2 kah?
subtitles.english: Is it Gen 1? Gen 2?

subtitles.original: Aku nggak tau, nggak mau kasih tebak!
subtitles.english: I don't know, I'm not going to guess!

subtitles.original: Ya udah makanya kalian nonton terus ya!
subtitles.english: Alright, so just keep watching!

subtitles.original: Siap ya, siap ya! Semangat semangat semangat!
subtitles.english: Ready? Ready? Let's go let's go!

subtitles.original: Satu, dua, tiga! hololive ID!
subtitles.english: One, two, three! hololive ID!

subtitles.original: Melompat Lebih Tinggi
subtitles.english: Jump Higher

subtitles.original: Kita berlari dan teruskan bernyanyi.
subtitles.english: We run and keep on singing.

subtitles.original: Kita buka lebar pelukan mentari.
subtitles.english: We open wide the embrace of the sun.

subtitles.original: Bila ku terjatuh nanti, kau siap mengangkat aku lebih tinggi.
subtitles.english: If I fall later, you're ready to lift me higher.

subtitles.original: Seperti perih yang telah kita bagi.
subtitles.english: Like the pain we have shared.

subtitles.original: Layaknya luka yang telah terobati.
subtitles.english: Like a wound that has been healed.

subtitles.original: Bila kita jatuh nanti, kita siap untuk melompat lebih tinggi.
subtitles.english: If we fall later, we are ready to jump higher.

subtitles.original: Bersama kita bagai hutan dan hujan.
subtitles.english: Together we are like forest and rain.

subtitles.original: Aku ada karena kau telah tercipta.
subtitles.english: I exist because you have been created.

subtitles.original: Kupetik bintang untuk kau simpan.
subtitles.english: I pluck a star for you to keep.

subtitles.original: Cahayanya tenang berikan kau perlindungan.
subtitles.english: Its calm light gives you protection.

subtitles.original: Sebagai pengingat teman juga sebagai jawaban.
subtitles.english: As a reminder, friend, and also as an answer.
